title: "JP Drivers Test Trainer — 外免切替 学習アプリ"
abstract: "Bilingual (EN/PT) offline-first study tool for the Japanese driver's license written exam (gaimen kirikae) and closed-course practical skill test. Features 1081+ true/false questions, timed mock exams, RAG-powered AI teacher via local Ollama, and maneuver walkthroughs."
